data.title: Did you know Ben Franklin had a common law marriage with his wife of 44 years, Deborah Read Franklin, but only spent two of the last 17...
data.meta_description:
111 likes, 1 comments - americanacorner on January 13, 2024: "Did you know Ben Franklin had a common law marriage with his wife of 44 years, Deborah Read Franklin, but only spent two of the last 17 together while he was living in England? Find out more about this and other untold stories, successes and sacrifices made by our founding generation in Tom Hand’s “An American Triumph.” Visit bit.ly/americantriumph to order today!
 
All proceeds help fund Americana Corner's Preserving America Grant Program.
 
#historynerd #booklaunch #historybooks #booknerd #history #americanhistory #ushistory #foundingfathers #benfranklin #johnadams #georgewashington #historybuff".
